#: ../../../HowToReleaseLLVM.rst:273
msgid ""
"https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/issues?"
"q=is%3Aissue+milestone%3A%22LLVM+14.0.5+Release%22+no%3Aproject+"
msgstr ""

